# Frontend Patterns

## Server State — TanStack Query

ALL data fetching goes through TanStack Query. Never use `useEffect` + `fetch`/`axios` directly.

```typescript
// ✅ Fetching data
const { data, isLoading } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['scenario-runs'],
  queryFn: () => scenariosApi.getRecent(20),
  refetchInterval: 5000,
});

// ✅ Mutations
const mutation = useMutation({
  mutationFn: scenariosApi.run,
  onSuccess: () => {
    queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['scenario-runs'] });
    toast({ title: 'Done' });
  },
  onError: (error) => {
    toast({ title: 'Error', variant: 'destructive' });
  },
});

// ❌ Forbidden
useEffect(() => {
  axios.get('/api/scenarios').then(setData);
}, []);
```

## Forms — React Hook Form + Zod

All forms use RHF with Zod schema validation.

```typescript
const schema = z.object({
  type: z.enum(['success', 'validation_error', 'system_error', 'slow_request']),
  name: z.string().optional(),
});

const { register, handleSubmit, formState: { errors } } = useForm<FormValues>({
  resolver: zodResolver(schema),
});
```

## UI Components — shadcn/ui

- Use components from `@/components/ui/` (already installed)
- Available: Button, Card, Input, Label, Badge, Select, Toast, Toaster
- For notifications: `useToast()` hook + `<Toaster />` in layout
- Loading states: use `disabled + Loader2` spinner on Button

## File Structure
- `src/app/` — Next.js App Router pages
- `src/components/ui/` — shadcn primitives (don't modify)
- `src/components/<domain>/` — feature components (e.g. `scenarios/`)
- `src/hooks/` — custom hooks
- `src/lib/api.ts` — all API calls via axios instance

## Styling
- Tailwind CSS only for layout and styling
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` to merge class names
- Color tokens via CSS variables (defined in `globals.css`)
